{
  "English": {
    "流花油田A03井插拔采油树面板，水深300米，使用Triton XLX ROV。": "Insertion and removal of the production tree panel at the Liuhua Oilfield A03 well, water depth 300 meters, using an autonomous underwater vehicle.",
    "您好！请描述您的水下作业任务，例如：\"流花油田A03井插拔采油树面板，水深300米，使用Triton XLX ROV\" 或 \"紧急巡检PL-003管线泄漏\"。": "Hello! Please describe your subsea operation, e.g., \"Insert subsea Christmas tree valve at Liuhua A03 wellhead, depth 300m, using Triton XLX ROV\" or \"Emergency pipeline inspection on leak of PL-003 pipeline\".",
    "今天天气很好，适合出海作业。": "The weather is great today, suitable for offshore operations.",
    "收到，已记录您的任务目标：**在流花 A03 井口进行采油树控制面板阀门插入作业**。\n\n为了确保任务参数规范且可行，我需要向您确认以下关键信息：\n\n1.  **作业时间**：请提供任务的**开始时间**和**结束时间**。\n2.  **经纬度坐标**：请提供流花 A03 井口的具体**北纬**和**东经**坐标。\n3.  **作业设备确认**：\n    *   您提到的\"Triton XLX\"不在我们当前支持的设备列表中。\n    *   **关键约束**：采油树阀门插拔属于重型干预作业，**强制要求使用“工作级 ROV\"**。\n    *   请从以下选项中确认您希望的作业设备全称：\n        *   `sealien_work_class` (工作级)\n        *   `sealien_cable_pipeline` (工作级)\n4.  **携带工具**：请从以下选项中选择本次作业需要携带的工具（可多选或单选）：\n    *   `液压扭矩工具`\n    *   `阀门操作接口工具`\n    *   `机械臂`\n    *   `清洁刷`\n    *   `防喷工具包`\n5.  **支持船选择**：请从以下可用船只中选择一艘：\n    *   `海洋石油 681` (深水综合作业船)\n    *   `DSV-Oceanic` (深水支持船)\n    *   `海洋石油 286` (综合物探船，但需注意其更适合观察作业，且当前任务强制要求工作级 ROV，请确认是否匹配)\n\n请补充以上信息，我将为您生成完整的任务参数并进行可行性验证。": "Received, your mission objective has been recorded: **performing Christmas tree control panel valve insertion operations at the Liuhua A03 wellhead**.\n\nTo ensure the mission parameters are standardized and feasible, I need to confirm the following key information:\n\n1.  **Operation Time**: Please provide the **start time** and **end time** for the task.\n2.  **Geographic Coordinates**: Please provide the specific **latitude** and **longitude** coordinates for the Liuhua A03 wellhead.\n3.  **Operation Equipment Confirmation**:\n    *   The \"Triton XLX\" you mentioned is not in our currently supported equipment list.\n    *   **Key Constraint**: Christmas tree valve insertion/removal belongs to heavy-duty intervention operations and **mandates the use of a \"Work-Class ROV\"**.\n    *   Please confirm the full name of the operation equipment you wish to use from the following options:\n        *   `sealien_work_class` (Work-Class)\n        *   `sealien_cable_pipeline` (Work-Class)\n4.  **Tools to Carry**: Please select the tools required for this operation from the following options (multiple or single selection allowed):\n    *   `Hydraulic Torque Tool`\n    *   `Valve Operation Interface Tool`\n    *   `Manipulator Arm`\n    *   `Cleaning Brush`\n    *   `Blowout Prevention Tool Kit`\n5.  **Support Vessel Selection**: Please select one vessel from the available options:\n    *   `CNOOC 681` (Deepwater Integrated Operation Vessel)\n    *   `DSV-Oceanic` (Deepwater Support Vessel)\n    *   `CNOOC 286` (Integrated Geophysical Survey Vessel; note that it is better suited for observation operations, and since the current task mandates a Work-Class ROV, please confirm if this matches)\n\nPlease supplement the above information, and I will generate the complete mission parameters and conduct a feasibility verification for you.",
    "收到，正在为您规划“流花油田 A03 井采油树控制面板插拔”任务。\n\n在继续收集剩余参数前，我必须先向您同步一个**关键安全警告**，请您务必确认：\n\n⚠️ **环境信息已过期**\n我们的海况数据最后更新于 **2026-06-30**，当前时间已是 **2026-07-09**，数据已超出有效范围，无法反映实时海况，可能严重影响作业安全。\n*   **建议**：请在更新最新环境数据后再执行任务，或确认是否忽略此风险继续（若忽略，系统会记录不再重复提醒）。\n\n---\n\n此外，关于您提到的设备信息，需要向您核实以下两点专业约束：\n\n1.  **关于 ROV 型号**：\n    您提到的\"Triton XLX\"在我们的作业库中暂未收录。目前针对“采油树控制面板插拔”这类需要机械臂和液压工具支持的重型作业，系统推荐且强制要求使用**工作级 ROV**。\n    *   已知可用型号：**专业级作业型 ROV**（最大水深 4000m，配备液压扭矩工具、阀门操作接口工具等）。\n    *   请确认是否将任务设备更换为 **专业级作业型 ROV**？\n\n2.  **关于任务时间**：\n    您尚未指定具体的**任务开始时间**和**结束时间**。\n    *   请提供计划开始作业的具体时间（例如：明天上午 10:00）。\n\n**待您确认上述设备替换方案及时间后，我将继续引导您填写以下缺失的关键信息：**\n*   油田经纬度坐标（流花油田具体坐标？）\n*   井口编号（A03 是编号吗？还是需要更详细的编码？）\n*   携带工具（从：液压扭矩工具、阀门操作接口工具、机械臂、清洁刷、防喷工具包 中选）\n*   支持船编号（从：海洋石油 681、DSV-Oceanic、海洋石油 286 中选）\n\n请回复确认，我们接着往下走。": "Received, planning the task \"Flowing Flower Oilfield Well A03 Christmas Tree Control Panel Plugging/Unplugging\" for you.\n\nBefore collecting the remaining parameters, I must first synchronize a **critical safety warning** with you. Please confirm:\n\n⚠️ **Environment Information Expired**\nOur sea state data was last updated on **2026-06-30**, while the current date is **2026-07-09**. The data has exceeded its validity period, cannot reflect real-time sea conditions, and may seriously affect operation safety.\n*   **Suggestion**: Please update the latest environment data before executing the task, or confirm whether to ignore this risk and proceed (if ignored, the system will record this and not remind again).\n\n---\n\nAdditionally, regarding the equipment information you mentioned, I need to verify the following two professional constraints:\n\n1.  **Regarding ROV Model**:\n    The \"Triton XLX\" you mentioned is not yet included in our operation library. For heavy-duty operations such as \"Christmas Tree Control Panel Plugging/Unplugging\" that require robotic arm and hydraulic tool support, the system recommends and mandates the use of a **Work-Class ROV**.\n    *   Available Model: **Professional Work-Class ROV** (Maximum water depth 4000m, equipped with hydraulic torque tools, valve operation interface tools, etc.).\n    *   Please confirm whether to replace the task equipment with a **Professional Work-Class ROV**?\n\n2.  **Regarding Task Time**:\n    You have not specified the specific **Task Start Time** and **End Time**.\n    *   Please provide the planned start time for the operation (e.g., tomorrow at 10:00 AM).\n\n**After you confirm the above equipment replacement plan and time, I will continue to guide you to fill in the following missing key information:**\n*   Oilfield latitude and longitude coordinates (Specific coordinates for Flowing Flower Oilfield?)\n*   Wellhead Number (Is A03 the number? Or is a more detailed code required?)\n*   Tools to Carry (Select from: Hydraulic Torque Tool, Valve Operation Interface Tool, Robotic Arm, Cleaning Brush, Blowout Preventer Tool Kit)\n*   Support Vessel Number (Select from: CNOOC 681, DSV-Oceanic, CNOOC 286)\n\nPlease reply to confirm, and we will proceed.",
    "流花油田A03井插拔采油树面板，水深300米，使用Triton XLX ROV": "Plugging and unplugging the production tree panel at Liuhua Oilfield Well A03, water depth 300 meters, using Triton XLX ROV",
    "收到，已记录您的任务需求：**在流花 A03 井口进行采油树控制面板阀门插入作业**，目标水深 300 米。\n\n不过，您在设备选型上提到了\"Triton XLX ROV\"，我需要向您核对并修正一个关键约束：\n根据作业安全规范，**采油树阀门插拔属于重型干预作业，必须使用“工作级 ROV\"（配备机械臂和液压工具）**，观察级或调查级 ROV 无法完成此任务。\n\n目前您尚未指定具体的支持船只和携带工具。为了推进任务规划，请确认以下信息：\n\n1.  **作业设备类型**：请确认选择 **“工作级 ROV\"**（是否有特定的工作级 ROV 型号偏好？系统内常见型号如 `sealien_work_class` 等，我将根据您的确认推荐具体型号）。\n2.  **支持船编号**：请从以下可用船只中选择一艘：\n    *   `海洋石油 681` (深水综合作业船，支持饱和潜水和 ROV 作业)\n    *   `DSV-Oceanic` (外籍深水支持船，主要承担深水 ROV 干预作业)\n    *   `海洋石油 286` (综合物探船，*注：此船主要用于观察作业，可能无法满足工作级 ROV 的部署需求，建议优先考虑前两艘*)\n3.  **携带工具**：请从以下选项中选择您需要的工具（可多选，如：`液压扭矩工具 `、`阀门操作接口工具`、`机械臂`、`清洁刷`、`防喷工具包`）：\n    *   建议组合：`液压扭矩工具 ` + `阀门操作接口工具` + `机械臂`\n\n此外，请补充以下时间信息以便生成任务计划：\n*   **任务开始时间**：(默认为当前时间 2026-02-06 04:44:37，如有特殊安排请指定)\n*   **任务结束时间**：\n\n请回复上述确认信息，我将为您完成参数规范化并生成最终任务工单。": "Received, your task requirements have been recorded: **performing valve insertion operations on the production tree control panel at Liuhua Wellhead A03**, with a target water depth of 300 meters.\n\nHowever, regarding your equipment selection of \"Triton XLX ROV\", I need to verify and correct a key constraint:\nAccording to operational safety regulations, **production tree valve insertion/removal is classified as heavy-duty intervention and must be performed using a \"Work-Class ROV\" (equipped with a manipulator and hydraulic tools)**. Observation-class or survey-class ROVs cannot complete this task.\n\nYou have not yet specified the support vessel or the tools to be carried. To advance the task planning, please confirm the following information:\n\n1.  **Operation Equipment Type**: Please confirm the selection of **\"Work-Class ROV\"** (Do you have a preference for a specific Work-Class ROV model? Common models in the system include `sealien_work_class`, etc., and I will recommend a specific model based on your confirmation).\n2.  **Support Vessel Number**: Please select one of the following available vessels:\n    *   `CNOOC 681` (Deepwater comprehensive operation vessel, supports saturation diving and ROV operations)\n    *   `DSV-Oceanic` (Foreign deepwater support vessel, primarily undertakes deepwater ROV intervention operations)\n    *   `CNOOC 286` (Comprehensive geophysical survey vessel, *Note: This vessel is primarily used for observation operations and may not meet the deployment requirements for Work-Class ROVs; it is recommended to prioritize the first two vessels*)\n3.  **Tools to Carry**: Please select the tools you need from the following options (multiple selections allowed, e.g., `Hydraulic Torque Tool`, `Valve Operation Interface Tool`, `Manipulator`, `Cleaning Brush`, `Blowout Prevention Tool Kit`):\n    *   Recommended Combination: `Hydraulic Torque Tool` + `Valve Operation Interface Tool` + `Manipulator`\n\nAdditionally, please provide the following time information to generate the task plan:\n*   **Task Start Time**: (Default is current time 2026-02-06 04:44:37; please specify if there are special arrangements)\n*   **Task End Time**:\n\nPlease reply with the above confirmation information, and I will complete the parameter normalization and generate the final task work order for you.",
    "Insert subsea Christmas tree valve at Liuhua A03 wellhead, depth 300m, using Triton XLX ROV": "Insert subsea Christmas tree valve at Liuhua A03 wellhead, depth 300m, using Triton XLX ROV",
    "理解您希望提高效率。作为专业的水下多智能体任务决策大模型，我可以基于行业标准和当前任务上下文，**推荐**最合理的默认值供您快速确认，但为了符合任务发布的严谨性，**关键参数（特别是设备型号、工具、船只）仍需您的最终确认**。\n\n基于您提供的信息（流花 A03 井口、300 米水深、采油树阀门插入），我为您生成了以下**推荐参数草案**：\n\n*   **任务开始时间**：`2026-02-06 04:50:00` (建议在当前可用时间稍后一点开始，预留准备时间)\n*   **任务结束时间**：`2026-02-06 12:50:00` (预估 8 小时作业窗口，含机动与操作时间)\n*   **油田名称**：`流花油田` (根据\"Liuhua A03\"推断)\n*   **油田经纬度坐标**：`北纬 20.0 度，东经 113.5 度` (该区域典型坐标，需您确认是否准确)\n*   **水深**：`300` 米\n*   **井口编号**：`A03`\n*   **作业设备类型**：`工作级 ROV` (强制要求，因任务性质)\n*   **作业设备全称**：`sealien_work_class` (推荐系统内标准工作级型号，具备机械臂和液压能力)\n*   **携带工具**：`液压扭矩工具`, `阀门操作接口工具`, `机械臂` (插拔阀门的标准工具组合)\n*   **支持船编号**：`海洋石油 681` (推荐：深水综合作业船，DP3 系统，最适合此深度和干预任务)\n\n---\n\n**请回复：**\n*   **确认**：“以上参数确认无误，请生成任务。” (如果全部接受)\n*   **修改**：指出需要修改的具体字段（例如：“船只改为 DSV-Oceanic\"或“坐标确认无误”）。\n\n一旦您确认，我将立即锁定参数并进入可行性验证阶段。": "I understand your desire to improve efficiency. As a professional underwater multi-agent task decision large model, I can **recommend** the most reasonable default values based on industry standards and the current task context for your quick confirmation. However, to comply with the rigor of task publishing, **key parameters (especially equipment models, tools, and vessels) still require your final confirmation**.\n\nBased on the information you provided (Liuhua A03 wellhead, 300m water depth, production tree valve insertion), I have generated the following **recommended parameter draft** for you:\n\n*   **Task Start Time**: `2026-02-06 04:50:00` (Suggested to start slightly later than the current available time to reserve preparation time)\n*   **Task End Time**: `2026-02-06 12:50:00` (Estimated 8-hour operation window, including maneuvering and operation time)\n*   **Oilfield Name**: `Liuhua Oilfield` (Inferred from \"Liuhua A03\")\n*   **Oilfield Latitude/Longitude Coordinates**: `20.0° N, 113.5° E` (Typical coordinates for this area; please confirm accuracy)\n*   **Water Depth**: `300` meters\n*   **Wellhead Number**: `A03`\n*   **Operation Equipment Type**: `Work-class ROV` (Mandatory requirement due to task nature)\n*   **Operation Equipment Full Name**: `sealien_work_class` (Recommended standard work-class model within the system, equipped with a manipulator and hydraulic capabilities)\n*   **Carried Tools**: `Hydraulic Torque Tool`, `Valve Operation Interface Tool`, `Manipulator` (Standard tool combination for valve insertion/removal)\n*   **Support Vessel Number**: `CNOOC 681` (Recommended: Deepwater comprehensive operation vessel, DP3 system, best suited for this depth and intervention task)\n\n---\n\n**Please reply:**\n*   **Confirm**: \"The above parameters are confirmed as correct; please generate the task.\" (If all are accepted)\n*   **Modify**: Point out the specific fields that need modification (e.g., \"Change vessel to DSV-Oceanic\" or \"Coordinates confirmed as correct\").\n\nOnce you confirm, I will immediately lock the parameters and proceed to the feasibility verification stage.",
    "你可以自动填充合理字段吗": "{\n  \"task_type\": \"采油树控制面板插入\",\n  \"task_type_key\": \"tree_valve_operation\",\n  \"emergency_mode\": false\n}",
    "收到，您计划对**流花 11-1 油田 A03 井**执行**采油树控制面板插入**作业，水深 300 米。\n\n但在任务规划中，我检测到一个**关键违规项**，需要立即向您确认：\n\n⚠️ **环境信息已过期**\n   环境信息最后更新于 `2026-06-30T16:00:00+08:00`，已超出有效时间范围，无法反映实时海况，可能影响作业安全，请更新环境信息后再继续。\n\n此外，关于您提到的设备 **Triton XLX ROV**，我们的知识库中未收录该型号的具体参数。根据【采油树阀门插拔】作业的强制约束（规则 C002），此类任务**必须使用工作级 ROV（Work-class ROV）**。\n*   已知符合要求的设备：**sealien_work_class**（工作级，最大水深 4000m，配备机械臂及液压工具）。\n*   请确认是否将设备更换为我们知识库中的 **sealien_work_class**？\n\n同时，为了推进任务，还需要您补充以下**待收集字段**：\n1.  **任务开始时间**（当前系统时间为 2026 年 07 月 20 日 18:32，时间不能早于此）\n2.  **任务结束时间**\n3.  **油田经纬度坐标**（例如：北纬 19.8 度，东经 113.5 度）\n4.  **携带工具**（请从以下选项中选择：`液压扭矩工具 `、`阀门操作接口工具 `、` 机械臂`、` 清洁刷`、` 防喷工具包`）\n5.  **支持船编号**（请从以下选项中选择：`海洋石油 681`、`DSV-Oceanic`、` 海洋石油 286`、` 海洋石油 708`）\n\n**您希望如何处理？**\n*   A. 更新环境信息并确认更换设备为 `sealien_work_class`，然后依次填写上述缺失字段。\n*   B. 先忽略环境过期警告，直接继续填写其他字段（系统记录后不再提醒）。\n*   C. 取消当前任务。\n\n请明确指示您的选择。": "Received. You plan to execute a **Christmas tree control panel insertion** operation on **Liuhua 11-1 Oilfield Well A03** at a water depth of 300 meters.\n\nHowever, during task planning, I detected a **critical violation** that requires your immediate confirmation:\n\n⚠️ **Environment Information Expired**\n   The environment information was last updated at `2026-06-30T16:00:00+08:00`, which exceeds the valid time range. It cannot reflect real-time sea conditions and may affect operation safety. Please update the environment information before proceeding.\n\nAdditionally, regarding the equipment **Triton XLX ROV** you mentioned, specific parameters for this model are not recorded in our knowledge base. According to the mandatory constraints for the **Christmas tree valve insertion/removal** operation (Rule C002), such tasks **must use a Work-class ROV**.\n*   Known compliant equipment: **sealien_work_class** (Work-class, max depth 4000m, equipped with manipulator and hydraulic tools).\n*   Please confirm whether to replace the equipment with **sealien_work_class** from our knowledge base?\n\nFurthermore, to proceed with the task, you need to provide the following **fields to be collected**:\n1.  **Task Start Time** (Current system time is July 20, 2026, 18:32; time cannot be earlier than this)\n2.  **Task End Time**\n3.  **Oilfield Latitude/Longitude Coordinates** (e.g., 19.8°N, 113.5°E)\n4.  **Tools to Carry** (Please select from the following options: `Hydraulic Torque Tool`, `Valve Operation Interface Tool`, `Manipulator`, `Cleaning Brush`, `Blowout Prevention Tool Kit`)\n5.  **Support Vessel Number** (Please select from the following options: `CNOOC 681`, `DSV-Oceanic`, `CNOOC 286`, `CNOOC 708`)\n\n**How would you like to proceed?**\n*   A. Update environment information and confirm replacing the equipment with `sealien_work_class`, then fill in the missing fields one by one.\n*   B. Ignore the environment expiration warning for now and proceed directly to fill in the other fields (the system will record this and not remind you again).\n*   C. Cancel the current task.\n\nPlease clearly indicate your choice.",
    "收到，正在为您规划“流花油田 A03 井采油树控制面板插拔”任务。\n\n在继续收集剩余参数前，我必须先向您同步一个**关键安全警告**，请您务必确认：\n\n⚠️ **环境信息已过期**\n我们的海况数据最后更新于 **2026-06-30**，当前时间已是 **2026-07-09**，数据已超出有效范围，无法反映实时海况，可能严重影响作业安全。\n*   **建议**：请在更新最新环境数据后再执行任务，或确认是否忽略此风险继续（若忽略，系统会记录不再重复提醒）。\n\n---\n\n此外，关于您提到的设备信息，需要向您核实以下两点专业约束：\n\n1.  **关于 ROV 型号**：\n    您提到的\"Triton XLX\"在我们的作业库中暂未收录。目前我们支持的设备类型包括：**观察级 ROV** 和**工作级 ROV**。\n    *   鉴于“采油树面板插拔”属于高风险干预作业，**强制要求使用工作级 ROV**（配备机械臂和液压工具）。\n    *   请问您是否选择使用我们库中的**工作级 ROV**？或者您有其他优先选择？\n\n2.  **关于携带工具**：\n    该任务必须从以下标准工具包中选择携带工具（单选）：\n    *   液压扭矩工具\n    *   阀门操作接口工具\n    *   机械臂\n    *   清洁刷\n    *   防喷工具包\n\n---\n\n**请您确认：**\n1. 是否忽略“环境信息过期”的警告？\n2. 确认使用的 ROV 型号（建议选工作级 ROV）？\n3. 选择需要携带的工具？\n\n确认后，我将引导您填写**任务时间**、**油田经纬度**、**井口编号**以及**支持船编号**。": "Received, planning the \"Flowing Flower Oilfield Well A03 Christmas Tree Panel Plugging/Unplugging\" task for you.\n\nBefore collecting the remaining parameters, I must first synchronize a **critical safety warning** with you. Please confirm:\n\n⚠️ **Environment Information Expired**\nOur sea state data was last updated on **2026-06-30**, and the current date is **2026-07-09**. The data has exceeded its validity period, cannot reflect real-time sea conditions, and may seriously affect operational safety.\n*   **Suggestion**: Please update the latest environmental data before executing the task, or confirm whether to ignore this risk and proceed (if ignored, the system will record this and not remind again).\n\n---\n\nAdditionally, regarding the equipment information you mentioned, we need to verify the following two professional constraints:\n\n1.  **Regarding ROV Model**:\n    The \"Triton XLX\" you mentioned is not yet included in our equipment library. Currently, the supported equipment types include: **Inspection-class ROV** and **Work-class ROV**.\n    *   Given that \"Christmas tree panel plugging/unplugging\" belongs to high-risk intervention operations, **Work-class ROV** (equipped with manipulators and hydraulic tools) is **mandatory**.\n    *   Would you like to select a **Work-class ROV** from our library? Or do you have other priority choices?\n\n2.  **Regarding Carried Tools**:\n    This task requires selecting tools from the following standard toolkits (single choice):\n    *   Hydraulic torque tool\n    *   Valve operation interface tool\n    *   Manipulator\n    *   Cleaning brush\n    *   Blowout preventer tool kit\n\n---\n\n**Please confirm:**\n1.  Whether to ignore the \"Environment Information Expired\" warning?\n2.  Confirm the ROV model to be used (Work-class ROV recommended)?\n3.  Select the tool to be carried?\n\nAfter confirmation, I will guide you to fill in the **Task Time**, **Oilfield Latitude/Longitude**, **Wellhead Number**, and **Support Vessel Number**.",
    "您好，收到您的任务规划意向：**在流花油田 A03 井进行采油树控制面板的插拔作业，水深 300 米，拟使用 Triton XLX ROV。**\n\n在正式确认任务参数前，系统检测到**一项关键的环境安全约束**，需要您立即确认处理方式：\n\n> **⚠️ 作业规范警告：环境信息已过期**\n> 当前环境数据最后更新于 `2026-06-30`，已超过有效时间范围。由于无法反映实时海况（如流速、浑浊度、海床质地等），直接执行任务存在安全隐患。\n\n**请您决策：**\n1. **更新环境信息**：联系现场支持团队获取最新实时海况数据，更新后再继续填写任务参数。\n2. **忽略警告继续**：若您确定现场条件允许且风险可控，选择忽略此警告，系统将继续引导您填写剩余参数（但请注意，这可能导致后续作业规划受限或触发更高级别阻断）。\n\n**请明确回复您的选择（更新或忽略）。**\n\n---\n*注：关于您提到的\"Triton XLX ROV\"，目前系统知识库中该型号暂无详细作业参数记录（如最大水深、载荷配置等）。若环境问题解决后继续，我将基于现有知识库为您匹配最匹配的**工作级 ROV**（如 Sealien Work Class），因为采油树面板插拔强制要求使用具备机械臂和液压工具的工作级设备。*": "Hello, we have received your task planning intent: **Performing plug-and-play operations on the Christmas tree control panel at Well A03 in the Liuhua Oilfield, at a water depth of 300 meters, with the planned use of a Triton XLX ROV.**\n\nBefore formally confirming the task parameters, the system has detected **one critical environmental safety constraint** that requires your immediate confirmation on how to proceed:\n\n> **⚠️ Operational Procedure Warning: Environmental Information Expired**\n> The current environmental data was last updated on `2026-06-30`, which exceeds the valid time range. As it cannot reflect real-time sea conditions (such as current speed, turbidity, seabed texture, etc.), directly executing the task poses safety risks.\n\n**Please make a decision:**\n1. **Update Environmental Information**: Contact the on-site support team to obtain the latest real-time sea condition data, then proceed to fill in the remaining task parameters after updating.\n2. **Ignore Warning and Continue**: If you are certain that on-site conditions permit and risks are controllable, choose to ignore this warning. The system will continue to guide you to fill in the remaining parameters (please note, however, that this may lead to restricted subsequent operation planning or trigger higher-level blockages).\n\n**Please clearly reply with your choice (Update or Ignore).**\n\n---\n*Note: Regarding the \"Triton XLX ROV\" you mentioned, the current system knowledge base has no detailed operational parameter records for this model (such as maximum water depth, payload configuration, etc.). If you proceed after resolving the environmental issue, I will match the most suitable **work-class ROV** (e.g., Sealien Work Class) for you based on the existing knowledge base, as plugging and unplugging the Christmas tree panel strictly requires the use of a work-class ROV equipped with a manipulator and hydraulic tools.*",
    "好的，已记录您的输入。为了完善水下任务规划，接下来请提供 **任务类型**。": "收到您的信息，请继续补充任务描述。",
    "继续": "收到您的信息，请继续补充任务描述。",
